description: Awe inspiring regional wraps and melts, made with the best and freshest ingredients. With spicy to cold and crispy bites, Everyone will have something that fits their taste. We also have veggie, and gluten free versions for our restricted diet patrons. Our wraps are made with love and are carefully crafted for your party or event. We use the freshest ingredients available to make sure you get the best! From Asia to Texas, our regional flavors will be sure to excite your taste buds!
name: Perhaps A Wrap?
